-- Fortis Healthcare to Add 1,400 Beds in India for Total of 7,000 This Year
-- Adi Narayan
-- 2010-08-06T09:38:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-06/fortis-healthcare-to-add-1-400-beds-in-india-for-total-of-7-000-this-year.html

          
          
             Fortis Healthcare Ltd. plans to add
1,400 beds in India in the year ending March 31, taking its
total to 7,000, said Vishal Bali, chief executive officer of the
Fortis Hospitals unit, on a conference call today.  
